io V2 前端实现主体，按文件用途分类，不按抽象概念自由发挥。\\n\\n```text\\nsrc/\\n  pageComponents/\\n  commonUiComponents/\\n  bis/\\n  stores/\\n  utils/\\n```\\n\\n### 4.1 pageComponents\\n\\n`src/pageComponents/` 放页面主组件、页面私有组件、页面私有 hooks 和页面样式。\\n\\n目录按 `app/` 路由分类：\\n\\n```text\\nsrc/pageComponents/\\n  home/\\n    index.tsx\\n    index.scss\\n    com/\\n    hooks/\\n  stories/\\n    index.tsx\\n    index.scss\\n    com/\\n    hooks/\\n  debugger/\\n    index.tsx\\n    index.scss\\n    com/\\n    hooks/\\n```\\n\\n规则：\\n\\n- `index.tsx` 是该页面主组件，不是 barrel。\\n- `index.scss` 是该页面主样式。\\n- `com/` 放页面私有展示组件。\\n- `hooks/`  [... omitted end of long line]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":81,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"started\",\"call_id\":\"call-fee492ea-5768-407f-a769-a5a6021dc9e2-14\\nfc_62bea711-859e-96cb-b909-d59f714ce55c_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"shellBis|stores/|layering|STRUCT-02\",\"path\":\"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/scripts/studio-quality\",\"caseInsensitive\":false,\"multiline\":false,\"toolCallId\":\"call-fee492ea-5768-407f-a769-a5a6021dc9e2-14\\nfc_62bea711-859e-96cb-b909-d59f714ce55c_2\",\"offset\":0}},\"hookAdditionalContexts\":[],\"toolCallId\":\"call-fee492ea-5768-407f-a769-a5a6021dc9e2-14\\nfc_62bea711-859e-96cb-b909-d59f714ce55c_2\",\"startedAtMs\":\"1784802349151\"},\"model_call_id\":\"dda7230a-b121-48f9-8620-1f733a844daa-3-kpwv\",\"session_id\":\"35dc3cce-69fb-4024-87a4-56d2194d9b5d\",\"timestamp_ms\":1784802349164}","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":82,"content":"[gbx] · 搜索 shellBis|stores/|layering|STRUCT-02 in scripts/studio-quality","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":85,"content":"{\"type\":\"tool_call\",\"subtype\":\"completed\",\"call_id\":\"call-fee492ea-5768-407f-a769-a5a6021dc9e2-14\\nfc_62bea711-859e-96cb-b909-d59f714ce55c_2\",\"tool_call\":{\"grepToolCall\":{\"args\":{\"pattern\":\"shellBis|stores/|layering|STRUCT-