{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-6721effb-fad1-4fec-838e-85bc83961d26-12\nfc_d9da2174-0ac2-93d0-b841-381b11d3cf4c_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md","offset":150},"result":{"success":{"content":"|------|------|\n| `@airpc/rpg-engine` | 仅 Server 门面；Client 禁任何 import |\n| `apps/studioV2` | **禁止** barrel `index.ts`；直引具体文件 |\n| 目录职责聚类 | 异责 ≥2 组且可分类文件 ≥4 → 分子目录 |\n| 测试 | 进 `tests/`；禁与业务树平放 |\n\n## 8. 依赖方向与硬门禁\n\n```text\npage / com      → shell bis, feature bis, MUI, scss（✗ stores ✗ ajaxProxy）\nfeature bis     → ajaxProxy, store write（✗ pageComponents ✗ next/navigation）\nshell bis       → ajaxProxy, store write, next/navigation（仅 shell）\nstore           ✗ bis ✗ ajaxProxy ✗ next/navigation\najaxProxy       → fetch / EventSource only\n```\n\n| ID | 约束 |\n|----|------|\n| `STUDIO-STRUCT-021` | UI（`pageComponents` / `commonUiComponents`）禁 import `stores/**`、`ajaxProxy/**` |\n| `STUDIO-STRUCT-022` | `stores/**` 禁 import bis / ajaxProxy / `next/navigation` |\n| `STUDIO-STRUCT-023` | 非 `*.shell.bis.ts` 且非 `*Flow.ts` 的 bis 禁 `next/navigation` |\n| `STUDIO-STRUCT-024` | bis 禁 value import `pageComponents` / `commonUiComponents` |\n\n存量违规登记于 `scripts/studio-quality/studio-v2-layering-baseline.json`（内容哈希）；**触碰即必须改合规**。禁止宽目录永久豁免。\n\n另见 Client/Server 隔离：`STUDIO-STRUCT-005` / `020`。\n\n## 9. 与引擎文档对齐\n\n| 概念 | 客户端落点 |\n|------|------------|\n| UserGate `userId` | layout shell → layout store；API 一律带此 id |\n| CallSession | debugger shell 灌快照；挂机后清空 session 切片 |\n| SSE 聊天 | feature bis 管流；store 只留 streaming 标志 |\n| canvas.layout | 画布运行时 + flush 进 editor store；引擎忽略 layout |\n| Memory | 不进大数组；短查询经 API |\n\n## 10. 落地顺序\n\n1. 规则 + 硬门禁 + baseline（本文档批次）  \n2. 新代码强制三角；旧页触碰即迁  \n3. 优先收口故事编辑器（双层 + shell/feature 拆分）  \n4. 库页（characters / users / assets / packages）逐页迁 store+shell  \n5. baseline 清零  \n\n## 11. 验收摘录\n\n- [ ] page/com 不直读 store、不直引 ajaxProxy  \n- [ ] store 无网络、无 navigation、不 import bis  \n- [ ] 列表/调试/编辑会话由 shell 灌入对应 domain store  \n- [ ] 编辑器保存前 flush；配置态不靠 page hook 自管  \n- [ ] `check:studio-structure` 含 021～024 绿（baseline 仅覆盖未触碰存量）  \n- [ ] Zustand 不当 Profile/Memory 真源  \n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":203,"fileSize":8915,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md","readRange":{"startLine":150,"endLine":203},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-6721effb-fad1-4fec-838e-85bc83961d26-12\nfc_d9da2174-0ac2-93d0-b841-381b11d3cf4c_1","startedAtMs":"1784855851011","completedAtMs":"1784855851243"},"model_call_id":"5e7972c0-716b-4ed6-b5ab-acf67fb0040c-3-30y6","session_id":"01778627-348c-46ca-a01f-aef27e82753d","timestamp_ms":1784855851180}
